tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE model_metrics (
    model_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name STRING,
    metric_name STRING,
    metric_value FLOAT,
    metric_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE model_metrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    accuracy FLOAT,
    precision FLOAT,
    recall FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE data_metrics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_name VARCHAR(255),
    data_size INT,
    data_type VARCHAR(50),
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
